import './i18n'

import React from 'react'
import { CookiesProvider } from 'react-cookie'
import ReactDOM from 'react-dom/client'

import App from './App'

const root = ReactDOM.createRoot(document.getElementById('root'))
root.render(
  <React.StrictMode>
    <CookiesProvider>
      <App />
    </CookiesProvider>
  </React.StrictMode>
)
